ada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada.html\">Study in Canada as an international student</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work.html\">Working in Canada as an international student</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation.html\">Work or live in Canada after you graduate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility.html\">Who can apply</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study.html\">Field of study requirement</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<nav class=\"provisional gc-subway\">\n<h1 id=\"gc-document-nav\">Work in Canada after you graduate</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study.html\">Field of study requirement</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study.html#gc-document-nav\">Field of study requirement</a>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/currently-eligible.html\">Currently eligible CIP codes</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/currently-eligible.html#gc-document-nav\">Currently eligible CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/agriculture-agri-food.html\">Agriculture and agri-food CIP codes</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/agriculture-agri-food.html#gc-document-nav\">Agriculture and agri-food CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/education.html\">Education CIP codes</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/education.html#gc-document-nav\">Education CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/health-care.html\">Health care and social services CIP codes</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/health-care.html#gc-document-nav\">Health care and social services CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/stem.html\">STEM CIP codes</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/stem.html#gc-document-nav\">STEM CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a class=\"hidden-xs hidden-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/trade.html\">Trade CIP codes</a>\n<a class=\"visible-xs visible-sm\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study/trade.html#gc-document-nav\">Trade CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a aria-current=\"page\" class=\"active\" href=\"#\">Transport CIP codes</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<h1 class=\"gc-thickline\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Field of study: Eligible CIP codes for transport</h1>\n<p><span class=\"label label-info\">Last updated: July 4, 2025</span></p>\n<p>Check below to find out which <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/study-canada/work/after-graduation/eligibility/field-of-study.html#cip_code\" target=\"_blank\">Classification of Instructional Programs (CIP) code</a> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-new-window\"></span><span class=\"wb-inv\">(opens in a new tab)</span> in the transport category is eligible for a post-graduation work permit (PGWP).</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-8\">\n<div id=\"filterTemplate\">\n<div class=\"form-group\">\n<label for=\"customSearchUI\">Enter your CIP code</label>\n<input class=\"form-control\" id=\"customSearchUI\" placeholder=\"XX.XXXX\" type=\"search\"/>\n</div>\n<p class=\"wb-fltr-info\"><span data-nbitem=\"\"></span> CIP code(s) found</p>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"list-unstyled wb-filter\" data-wb-filter='{\n  \"uiTemplate\": \"#filterTemplate\",\n  \"selector\": \"&gt; li\"\n}' id=\"cip-list\">\n<li><div id=\"440403\">\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\">Public transportation and infrastructure planning/studies</h2>\n<p><strong>CIP code:</strong> 44.0403</p>\n<div class=\"well well-sm\">\n<div class=\"panel mrgn-bttm-0\">\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p class=\"text-center mrgn-tp-sm\">Your CIP code is eligible.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></li>\n<li><div id=\"470607\">\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"mrgn-tp-sm\">Airframe mechanics and aircraft maintenance technology/technician</h2>\n<p><strong>CIP code:</strong> 47.06